									<a rel="nofollow" class="cat-post-thumbnail  cat-post-none" href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/society/public-health/mental-health-outbreaks-coronavirus/" rel="bookmark" title="How infectious disease outbreaks affect mental health: Insights for coronavirus coverage">
